    "description": "<br><br>IRON GUARD VR是一款本着经典RTS游戏精神制作的科幻塔防游戏。幸存人员的生命掌握在你手中。找出terraformer机器人叛乱的原因，并帮助你的人员从一个未知的星球上撤离，在那里生存是新的前沿。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872200/extras/caca5e521ec22a68b21e1269cdc28e85.poster.avif?t=1747311204\" width=600 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872200/extras/caca5e521ec22a68b21e1269cdc28e85.webm?t=1747311204\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872200/extras/caca5e521ec22a68b21e1269cdc28e85.mp4?t=1747311204\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>特征：</strong><br><br>身临其境的自上而下的游戏玩法。<br><br>不同的游戏模式和风格<br><br>多个可升级的炮塔、路径阻拦器、采矿收割机。<br><br>任务之间非线性设备升级的可能性。<br><br>使用常规或超级武器从可升级的无人机进行街机式射击。<br><br>通过过场动画和对话揭示的独特故事情节。<br><br>惊艳的配音和音乐，以经典RTS游戏的真实风格为游戏玩法增添乐趣。<br><br>美丽而风格化的环境，带有未知星球的神秘气氛，展示发生战斗的各种生物群落。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872200/extras/c8f193fa148e4822d410887f583ff760.poster.avif?t=1747311204\" width=600 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872200/extras/c8f193fa148e4822d410887f583ff760.webm?t=1747311204\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872200/extras/c8f193fa148e4822d410887f583ff760.mp4?t=1747311204\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>故事：</strong><br><br>这一年是公元2232年，“Avalon”号的船员坠毁在Akris星球上，同时试图调查为何较早载有人工智能terraformer机器人的无人驾驶飞船失去联系。幸运的是，这个星球是宜居的，因为改造飞船和它的人工智能机器人已经完成了他们的工作，使“Akris”适合居住和可持续的生活。你是Graves副驾驶.你有责任保护幸存船员的生命。保护所有资源免受失控的terraformer机器人攻击。<br><br>使用工程无人机，架设防御炮塔，建造各种结构并收集资源。你需要不惜一切代价生存下去，以找出导致Terraformers失控并没有完成地球改造的原因。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872200/extras/d4f76eb631d6b64500b6b8c4a3d88820.poster.avif?t=1747311204\" width=600 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872200/extras/d4f76eb631d6b64500b6b8c4a3d88820.webm?t=1747311204\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872200/extras/d4f76eb631d6b64500b6b8c4a3d88820.mp4?t=1747311204\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
